{"tid":1485783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[撚狗成功] 政府就維園集會作出回應","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T04:48:22.000Z","uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6646d3461ae5613a1dd011fb678057853c238b80","tid":1485783,"uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"政府就維園集會作出回應<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（八月十八日）回應在維多利亞公園舉辦的公眾集會時表示，雖然集會期間大致和平，但由於參與者佔用了港島多條主要幹道，路面交通大受影響，對市民造成不便。運輸署與警方已積極協調，盡量將影響減至最少。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　發言人重申，目前最重要的是要盡快回復社會秩序；當一切平靜之後，政府會與市民展開真誠對話，致力修補撕裂，重建社會和諧。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月18日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時18分"},{"pid":"3b144b58765a727d0d9343e688579c00df1ff525","tid":1485783,"uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"無野講攞野黎講，阻路係d狗安排不周炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e05e8c8517833be9f32cbc2564f8490d10638aa","tid":1485783,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"還返隻眼俾我！真你老母誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b476f0194cc51d72ceec9fbb326311f48b875452","tid":1485783,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be85ef83b9e9181cbcc56d2ab4e9d9256f965455","tid":1485783,"uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b476f0194cc51d72ceec9fbb326311f48b875452","tid":1485783,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:45:56.000Z","msg":"Ching做乜考古"},{"pid":"c79b401029404ba509b4c58bbcc986fd47518cc0","tid":1485783,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be85ef83b9e9181cbcc56d2ab4e9d9256f965455","tid":1485783,"uid":140655,"like